        "### Visualizing Keyword Frequency\n",
        "This cell calculates the frequency of each keyword and creates a horizontal bar chart of the top 50 terms. This helps identify which specific words dominate the crisis communication landscape in this dataset."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 1000
